Poor, sweet boy, worked to death by your family.

32
00:01:15,130 --> 00:01:17,580
你生命的每一天
Every day of your life,

33
00:01:18,030 --> 00:01:20,630
令你無權埋葬在教堂的墓地里
making you unfit for burial in the churchyard,

34
