Alice.

36
00:01:27,730 --> 00:01:29,290
分娩而死
Died in child birth,

37
00:01:29,290 --> 00:01:32,040
懷上了你舅父的孩子
pregnant from your mother's brother.

38
00:01:33,710 --> 00:01:35,800
孩子在那兒
There. There, the baby.

39
00:01:39,610 --> 00:01:42,020
