Smothered to hide the evidence.

40
00:01:47,050 --> 00:01:49,500
讓他們母子不再分離
Let mother and child be together.

41
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:55,450
現在我是你們的母親
I am your mother now.

42
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,750
你們所有人的母親
All of you!

43
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,530
你們都是我的孩子
And you all are my children.

44
00:02:01,530 --> 00:02:03,450
我父親路易絲牧師說
My father, the good Reverend Lewis,

45
00:02:03,450 --> 00:02:05,330
