Perhaps more alive than any of us.

53
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:27,190
只不過你像只幽魂一樣隱藏自己
Yet you have hidden yourself like a ghost.

54
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:30,210
英克里斯到處在找你
Increase searches everywhere for you.

55
00:02:31,050 --> 00:02:32,990
