He will never look here.

56
00:02:32,990 --> 00:02:34,480
但我的姑娘們
But my girls.

57
00:02:35,140 --> 00:02:36,870
我那些可憐的姑娘們怎么辦
What of my poor girls?

58
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,240
他抓了她們四個
He has four of them.

59
00:02:39,610 --> 00:02:41,800
但不要擔心
But do not fear for them or yourself.

60
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:45,310
很快我們的大祭典將凈化這片土地上
Soon our grand rite will cleanse this land of the evil men do

61
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:47,100
一切邪惡的人和事
and the men who do it,

62
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:49,070
就像圣經時代的大洪水
like the great flood of biblical times,

63
00:02:49,070 --> 00:02:51,460
開辟通往我們新世界的道路
making way for our new world.

64
00:02:52,190 --> 00:02:53,850
放心吧  梅西
And rest assured, Mercy...

65
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:56,640
你和你的姑娘們
you, your girls,

66
00:02:57,180 --> 00:03:00,270
還有你的孩子們都會有立足之地
and all your children shall have a place there.

67
00:03:03,970 --> 00:03:05,480
謝謝你
Oh, thank you.

68
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,730
但請告訴我
But tell me...

69
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:12,830
好讓我消除他們的疑慮
tell me so I may reassure them in their fear.

70
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:13,930
到底是什么
What is it?

71
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:16,270
什么將會來臨
What is coming?

72
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,200
