*Witch drums*

75
00:03:40,940 --> 00:03:44,510
*擂我戰鼓*
*Pound me the witch drums*

76
00:03:44,890 --> 00:03:47,720
*擂我戰鼓*
*Pound me the witch drums*

77
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:48,940
*鼓鳴震天*
*The witch drums*

78
00:03:48,940 --> 00:03:51,440
*寧入地獄*
*Better pray for hell*

79
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:57,610
*不留人間*
*Not hallelujah*

80
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:22,600
這是一個古老的真理
'tis an ancient proverbial truth

