but the malum.

86
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,880
蘋果的圖像出現在
The icon of the apple

87
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:42,150
我們所了解的大祭典書里的每一頁
runs through almost every image we have of the grand rite.

88
00:04:43,170 --> 00:04:44,950
大祭典會帶來死亡
The grand rite brings about death,

89
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:48,290
大規模的死亡
death on a mass scale.

90
00:04:49,850 --> 00:04:51,350
對于它的操作  我們知之甚少
We know little of its operation,

91
00:04:51,350 --> 00:04:53,430
更別說它將
nor the...the mechanism of magic

92
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:56,500
如何帶來死亡
that unleashes the... the death that follows.

