誰啊
Yes?

106
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:38,800
麥哲牧師
Reverend Mather?

107
00:05:40,170 --> 00:05:41,660
我知道很晚了
I know it is late.

108
00:05:48,140 --> 00:05:49,360
這么晚你還在外面干嘛
What are you doing out?

109
00:05:49,850 --> 00:05:50,880
抱歉
I'm sorry.

110
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:53,090
我不知道還能找誰
I didn't know who else to turn to.

111
00:05:53,090 --> 00:05:54,610
你是唯一能幫助我的
You are the only one who can help me.

112
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:58,740
那你就來對了
Well, then you did the right thing by coming.

113
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:04,170
我要怎么幫你  幫你干什么
Uh...how may I help you, and...and with what?

114
00:06:04,180 --> 00:06:07,110
你覺得有可能嗎  一個人身為巫師
Do you think it's possible to be a witch

115
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:08,850
卻不自知
and not even know it?

116
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:13,520
我想若是他把靈魂交給了撒旦
I-I think one would know

117
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:16,480
他應該是知道的
if one had...deeded one's soul to satan.

118
