不  我不要你的保證
No. I want more than your assurance.

121
00:06:24,130 --> 00:06:24,890
我要...
I want...

122
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:32,320
我要你現在就檢查一下我
I want you to examine me now...

123
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:34,560
看看我有沒有惡魔之印記
for the mark of the devil.

124
00:06:36,470 --> 00:06:37,870
然后你就能向我保證了
Then, you may assure me.

125
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:18,990
我感覺不到惡魔的跡象
I feel no sign of satan.

126
00:07:19,550 --> 00:07:21,640
在我看來  你各個方面
You seem, to me, in every respect,

127
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,230
都沒有被惡魔侵襲
unmolested by the devil.

128
00:07:25,030 --> 00:07:25,890
我向你保證  霍爾小姐
I assure you, Miss Hale,

129
00:07:25,890 --> 00:07:27,730
如果你是巫師  你肯定會知道的
If you were a witch, you would know it.

130
00:07:40,770 --> 00:07:43,290
不要問此鐘為誰而鳴
Ask not for whom the bell tolls.

131
00:07:43,290 --> 00:07:44,870
它是為...
It tolls for...

132
00:07:46,470 --> 00:07:48,490
誰是第一個呢
I wonder who will be first.

133
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:50,110
是誰呢
Who will it be?

134
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:53,400
你是什么意思
What do you mean?

135
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:56,800
開口的人就不用遭受燒灼之痛
Whoever will speak will not burn.

136
00:07:57,270 --> 00:07:58,090
很簡單
Simple.

137
